<strong>REFERENCE LIST ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference list at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Producer(s). (Publication date). <em>Title of work</em> [Medium of publication]. Country of 
	origin: Studio.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Producer(s)">Jones, A. (Producer), &amp; Smith, A. (Director)</span>. 
	(<span class="hover" title="Publication date">2056</span>). 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of work">Outside the lines</span></em> 
	[<span class="hover" title="Medium of publication">Motion picture</span>]. 
	<span class="hover" title="Country of origin">Parramatta, Australia</span>: 
	<span class="hover" title="Studio">Upbeat Pictures</span>.
</blockquote>
