<strong>IN&#45;TEXT CITATION</strong>
<br>
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	Jones and Smith (2056) indicated that&hellip;
	<br>
	Alternatively: A recent study (Jones &amp; Smith, 2056) showed that&hellip;
</blockquote>
<br>
When the producer is referred to more than once in the same paragraph do not include the date 
in subsequent references, as long as the study cannot be confused with others cited.
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	In a recent study, Jones &amp; Smith (2056) showed that&hellip; Jones &amp; Smith 
	also found that&hellip;
</blockquote>
